-- FACTBOX: Buyers of delayed Boeing Dreamliner
-- 
-- Thu Dec 11, 2008 11:04am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/11/us-boeing-787-orders-idUSTRE4BA4LA20081211

 

 (Reuters) - Boeing Co ( BA.N ) pushed back the schedule for its troubled 787 Dreamliner for the fourth time on Thursday, making its new plane almost two years late and further angering airline customers and risking cancellations. 

